Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.96,SIGN,,0,0,0,,{\fs72\pos(369,366)}Resurrection
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuzaki, let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:08.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜崎、私に行かせてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,局長、私も行きます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかりました
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that you're dealing with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:14.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手はキラです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Under no circumstances should you let him see your face, and exercise extreme caution while restraining him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:18.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対顔を見せず、細心の注意を払って捕まえてください
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari, if Higuchi makes even one suspicious move...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワタリ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火口が少しでも妙な動きをしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll immobilize him without actually killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:23.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll immobilize him without actually killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺さぬ程度に動きを止めます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aizawa, did you bring something to obscure your face with?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:34.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相沢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:36.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔を隠す物の用意はあるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.81,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:37.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Back us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,援護をしてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood! {\alpha&HFF&}Thank you very much, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:41.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood! Thank you very much, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:43.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます、局長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi, put both hands up and step out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:50.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火口、両手を挙げ、車から降りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi has been secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:05.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火口を確保した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi-san, as we planned, place the transceiver on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:08.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,模木さん、手筈通り、火口にレシーバーを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:08.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs1} {\fnMonotype Corsiva\fe120\fs24\pos(485,375)}receiver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi, {\alpha&HFF&}how were you killing people? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:12.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi, how were you killing people? {\alpha&HFF&}Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやって殺人をしてきた、言うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi, how were you killing people? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, we'll make you confess using any means at our disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:22.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言わなければ、どんな手を使ってでも言わせます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…ノートだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:30.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノート？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably won't believe me, but if you write the name of a person whose face you know in that notebook, that person will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:32.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じられないだろうが…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:38.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔を知っている人間の名前を書くと、\N書かれた人間が死ぬノートだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:40.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノート…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:42.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜神さん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I've found it in his bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:43.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火口のバックの中にあった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true there are names written here, {\alpha&HFF&}but there's nothing unusual about this note--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:48.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに人の名前は書いてあるが…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true there are names written here, but there's nothing unusual about this note--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,格別変わったノートでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yagami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:56.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしました？夜神さん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}Monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ば…化物…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami-san, you aren't carrying a gun at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:01:59.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着いてください
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Yagami-san, you aren't carrying a gun at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:03.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜神さんは今拳銃を所持していません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ…そうだった…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫ですか？局長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}Mogi! Can't you see that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:10.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,も…模木、あれが見えないのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mogi! {\alpha&HFF&}Can't you see that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mogi! Can't you see that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, you're very tired at the moment--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,局長…疲れてるんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening, Mogi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだ、模木さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}Ah... I-It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ah... {\alpha&HFF&}I-It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ah... I-{\alpha&HFF&}It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:22.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ、これは…\Nどうやらノートを触った者でしか見えないらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ah... I-It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... {\alpha&HFF&}this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ah... I-It looks like only those who've touched this notebook can see this... this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ば…化物が…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bring that notebook to the helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:30.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのノートをヘリに持ってきてください
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:31.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…はい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you possibly be planning, Yagami Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体どうする気だ、夜神月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,By touching a Death Note that you previously owned, {\alpha&HFF&}all your memories associated with it will be recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:40.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前がノートを再び手にすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By touching a Death Note that you previously owned, all your memories associated with it will be recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:46.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,所有権があった時のデスノートの記憶全てが…甦る事にはなるが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:48.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuzaki, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:51.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜崎、これです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a Shinigami... {\alpha&HFF&}they really do... exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死神…ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a Shinigami... they really do... {\alpha&HFF&}exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:07.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に…いた…んですね…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a Shinigami... they really do... exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:09.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノート…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,青山でノートを見せる…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Showed each other our notebooks in Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Love at first sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一目惚れしたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuzaki, give me the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜崎、僕にもノートを…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's method of killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺人の手段…キラ、第二…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira... the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Two notebooks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:17.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二冊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,More than one notebook exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノートは二冊以上存在している…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ終わってない…
