Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:00.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜崎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:01.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, we've got to compare the names written here against the list of victims.
