Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm... {\alpha&HFF&}yes... I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？…はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm... yes... {\alpha&HFF&}I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm... yes... I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ…そうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs30}計画通り…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relinquishing all ownership of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:33.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このノートの所有権を…放棄する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The ownership of this notebook now returns to Rem. {\alpha&HFF&}Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:38.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでこのノートの所有権はレムに戻った…そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The ownership of this notebook now returns to Rem. Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. {\alpha&HFF&}Your point being?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ、しつこいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. Your point being?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now give that notebook to Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ、そのノートをリュークにあげてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of this notebook is now Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでそのノートの所有権はリュークになった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk, next, I want you to drop that notebook here, onto the ground of the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リューク
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:57.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをまた人間界の地に、今そこに落としてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, guess it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？…まあ、いいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the ownership returns to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでまた所有権は僕だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:07.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ownership has gone round in a circle; nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一周しただけで何も変わってないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、そうかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But there'll be a time when this will be of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしこれが必ず役に立つ時が来る…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And the first notebook that I received from Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:19.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして僕が最初にもらったこのノート…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving it back to you, and I want you to give it to Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度はこれをリュークに返すから、レムにあげてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:28.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem, I'll need you to pass that to someone who has a reasonably high status, yet remains greedy for success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:35.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レム
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:42.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをある程度の地位があり、\N出世欲が強く、その為に使うであろう人間に渡すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who'll undoubtedly use the notebook to further those goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing this will guarantee Misa's release from imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:48.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをすれば必ず海砂は…今の監禁から解放される
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If she still hasn't been released after several years, kill me. {\alpha&HFF&}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何年たっても解放されない様なら僕を殺せ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If she still hasn't been released after several years, kill me. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでそうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami Light, {\alpha&HFF&}what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:58.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜神月、何を考えている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami Light, what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all to save Misa. {\alpha&HFF&}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂を助ける為だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all to save Misa. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:01.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕を信用しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood... {\alpha&HFF&}if this will help Misa, I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood... if this will help Misa, I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:10.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂が助かるなら、言う通りにしてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I'll manipulate the situation so, like Misa, I'll be detained and under 24-hour surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕はこのあと、海砂のように監禁され
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２４時間監視状態になるよう仕向ける
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,While in detention, I'll relinquish all ownership of the Death Note and it'll erase any associated memories I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その状態でノートの所有権を放棄し
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デスノートに関する記憶を全て無くす…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,During that time, the judging of criminals will recommence, and if that continues, at some stage, Ryuuzaki will be forced to release us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その間に犯罪者裁きは復活し
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが続けば…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜崎はいつかは二人を解放せざるをえなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, with my memories gone, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sure I'll attempt to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして記憶を失った僕は…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, with my memories gone, I'm sure I'll attempt to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:43.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ずキラを捕まえようとするだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the type of person I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕はそういう人間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you plan to find the person Rem gives the notebook to before L can, and reclaim the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:52.55,Default-ja,,0,0,4,,そして{\fs8} {\fnCloister Black\fe120\fs30}L{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs14} {\fs24}より先に、\Nレムがノートを渡す奴を捕まえ、ノートを奪うってことか…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. {\alpha&HFF&}And I'll kill whoever has ownership of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:53.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. And I'll kill whoever has ownership of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてその時のノートの持ち主を殺す…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is one problem:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし問題がひとつある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hold no ownership over that Death Note, your memories will only return as long as you're physically touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:05.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,所有権を持っていなければ、\N記憶が戻るのはノートに触っている間だけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you let go, all your memories will be erased once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手を放せばまた、全ての記憶がなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to kill Higuchi without letting go of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:16.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このノートから手を放さないまま…火口を殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, the ownership will pass to me, and my memories won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:20.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすれば所有権は僕に移り、記憶は消えない…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I pull this four times with less than a second between each...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここを一秒以上の間隔を開けずに四回引く…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Success! {\alpha&HFF&}I knew I'd be wearing this at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:29.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Success! I knew I'd be wearing this at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:32.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり僕はこの時計をつけていた…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Old habits die hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,習慣ってものは変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami-san, please escort Higuchi to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜神さん、火口を車へお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,O-{\alpha&HFF&}Okay... understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…ああ…、わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay... {\alpha&HFF&}understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay... understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}if analyzed scientifically, I wonder if we'd discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:02.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このノート
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:03.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This notebook... if analyzed scientifically, {\alpha&HFF&}I wonder if we'd discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,科学分析とかしたら、何か出るだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This notebook... if analyzed scientifically, I wonder if we'd discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami-kun, that's not like you. {\alpha&HFF&}That thing is beyond science.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜神君らしくないですね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami-kun, that's not like you. That thing is beyond science.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,科学なんて超えてますよ、それは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:14.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はは…それもそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the longest 40 seconds of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生のうちで、一番長い{\fs8} {\fnDeath font\fe120\fs24}40{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs14} {\fs24}秒だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi! {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki! Higuchi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:47.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火口…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi! Ryuuzaki! {\alpha&HFF&}Higuchi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜崎、火口が…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi! Ryuuzaki! Higuchi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…何だ!?どうしたんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Higuchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…おい、火口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な…何をやっているんだ、父さん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, father?! {\alpha&HFF&}If Higuchi dies now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, father?! If Higuchi dies now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:00.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしここで、火口に死なれでもしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}This isn't possible... but I think he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま…まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This isn't possible... {\alpha&HFF&}but I think he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This isn't possible... but I think he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや、しかし…これはもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, {\alpha&HFF&}he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:09.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…死んでるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The next, Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は竜崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The next, Ryuuzaki... will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おまえだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"How to use"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs8} {\fnDeath font\fe120\fs24}HOW TO USE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"The human whose name is written in this note shall die."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:10:00.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このノートに名前を書かれた人間は…死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"This note will not take effect unless the writer has the person's face in their mind when they write his/her name."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,書かれる人物の顔が頭に入っていないと効果はない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:10.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,故に、同姓同名の人物に、一遍に効果は得られない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Therefore, people sharing the same name will not be affected."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"If the cause of death is written within 40 seconds of writing the person's name, it will happen as it is written."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:15.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名前のあとに人間界単位で…{\fs8} {\fnDeath font\fe120\fs24}40{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs14} {\fs24}秒以内に死因を書くと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:16.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その通りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"If the cause of death is not specified, by default, the person will die of a heart attack."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:20.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死因を書かなければ…全ては心臓麻痺になる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Should a cause of death be specified, a further 6 minutes and 40 seconds are granted to write any further details."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:25.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死因を書くとさらに{\fs8} {\fnDeath font\fe120\fs24}6{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs14} {\fs24}分{\fs8} {\fnDeath font\fe120\fs24}40{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs14} {\fs24}秒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:29.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,詳しい死の状況を記載する時間が与えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, in the "How to use"-section at the back, it states:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:37.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに、裏表紙の方の…{\fs8} {\fnDeath font\fe120\fs24}HOW TO USE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you make this note unusable by tearing it up or burning it, all the humans who have touched the note till then will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このノートを刻む役などして使えなくするとは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それまでにノートに触れた全ての人間が死ぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}Is that true, Aizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:47.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Is that true, Aizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.87,ps-ja,,0,0,0,,ほ…本当ですか、相沢さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:51.22,ps-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、そう書いてある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.69,Background,,0,0,0,,Yup, it's written right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that while that rule exists, they won't destroy the notebook, and there's no danger of me losing my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:50.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:54.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういう掟があれば、父さん達にノートを処分され
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.47,Background,,0,0,0,,Aw.. that's just shit... why didn't you tell me this earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.09,ps-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな～先に言ってくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.73,ps-ja,,0,0,0,,だって知らないでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の記憶がなくなる事もない…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem, I won't get in trouble with the old man for writing in fake rules, will I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レム
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:04.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに嘘のルール書いても、大王に怒られるわけないよな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:04.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs12\pos(375,370)}じじい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there are no rules regarding that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、そんな掟はない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then. {\alpha&HFF&}But Light, I'm counting on you for more apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:08.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライト、またリンゴ頼むぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then. But Light, I'm counting on you for more apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't have said "I want to see the Shinigami too", and touched that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:14.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「僕も死神見たい」なんて触らなければよかったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't, you'd be the only one in the investigation not knowing what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:23.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは、どう捜査になっているか、松田だけがわからなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:23.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでもいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ…僕も皆と同じ立場で捜査したいです、はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I want to be on the same level as everyone else in this investigation. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And this final sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして…この最後の一文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"If the person using the note fails to continuously write names of people to be killed within 13 days of each other, then the user will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このノートに名前を書き込んだ人間は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとも新しく名前を書いた時から、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:46.90,Default-ja,,0,0,4,,{\fs8} {\fnDeath font\fe120\fs24}13{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs14} {\fs24}日以内に次の名前を書き込み、人を殺し続けなければ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! {\alpha&HFF&}This means that both Light-kun and Misa-Misa are completely cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ってことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! This means that both Light-kun and Misa-Misa are completely cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:57.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで月君もミサミサも、完全に白ってことですね？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Light-kun and Amane were imprisoned for over 50 days, and even now are under surveillance. {\alpha&HFF&}If either were Kira, they'd no longer be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:03.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５０日以上監禁され、今も監視下にある月君と弥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Light-kun and Amane were imprisoned for over 50 days, and even now are under surveillance. If either were Kira, they'd no longer be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:07.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二人がキラなら、今生きているはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great news, isn't it, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかったですね、局長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:10.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem-san... {\alpha&HFF&}wasn't it? The white person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:12.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レムさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rem-san... wasn't it? The white person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でしたね、そこの白い方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ryuuzaki, that's rude! You can't go around calling them "white".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,り、竜崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失礼じゃないですか、白いとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other Death Notes in the human world, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノートは他にも人間界にありますね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure. Maybe there are, maybe there aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるかもしれないし、ないかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If other notebooks did exist, {\alpha&HFF&}would the rules be the same for all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし他のノートが存在していたら…\N全てのノートのルールは同じですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If other notebooks did exist, would the rules be the same for all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Ryuuzaki. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way that Rem will let you cast doubt upon these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無駄だよ竜崎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Ryuuzaki. There's no way that Rem will let you cast doubt upon these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このルールーはレムから絶対崩せない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they'd be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many notebooks within the world of Shinigami, but the rules are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:47.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノートは死神界にいくらでもあるが、ルールは全て同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Those notebooks under human possession also share a common set of rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間に持たせた時のルールもだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}the suspicions surrounding Light-kun and Amane have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:51.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜崎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuzaki, the suspicions surrounding Light-kun and Amane have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月君と弥の疑いは晴れた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to end their surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二人の監視は終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, it's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:12:59.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう明白ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:02.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…そうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:14.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかりました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for everything up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで申し訳ありませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:23.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:24.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But the case is still far from solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:28.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしまだ、この事件は完全解決とは言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Although these handcuffs will be removed, I'll continue to investigate from here, if that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手錠は外させてもらうが、ここで捜査を続けていいな？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:33.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Misa and I are 100% clear of suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:39.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで僕と海砂は…１００％白だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rules written by a Shinigami in a Death Note... {\alpha&HFF&}you'd have to believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死のノートに、死神によって書かれたルール…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rules written by a Shinigami in a Death Note... you'd have to believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが信じるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the fake rules I created, Ryuuzaki has nowhere to go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の作った嘘のルールによって…竜崎は手立てを失った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand this Ryuuzaki: {\alpha&HFF&}in any world, rules are something that are made by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.27,Kira in Shadow-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか竜崎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:58.59,Kira in Shadow-ja,,0,0,0,,ルールとはいつの世界も…神とされる者によって作られる物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand this Ryuuzaki: in any world, rules are something that are made by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You will bow down to the rules I've created.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:04.33,Kira in Shadow-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は僕の作ったルールに平伏し、\N新世界の神に逆らおうとした罪で…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to oppose me, the new god of this world, and for your transgression, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:05.79,Kira in Shadow-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! Promise me that you'll text me every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライト…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対毎日メールしてね…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:14.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うううう…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that I finally have to part with Misa-Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついにミサミサとももう別れか…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい、松田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, Matsuda, leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:19.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二人きりに！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya, Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあね、ミサミサ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we can be seen on the security cameras, from this angle, they shouldn't be able to see my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:31.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この角度なら、\N監視カメラに見られていたとしても、僕の口は映らない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, when you're certain that no one else is around, I want you to go to the place I'm about to tell you and dig up something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:32.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:38.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今から言う場所に埋めてある物を、\N絶対誰も見ていない時に…一人で掘り出してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! Your memories have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライト…記憶戻ったのね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫、海砂うまくやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Misa will do good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, I remember! {\alpha&HFF&}Everything that happened back when I was using this notebook... You must have buried this notebook so that I'd remember too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライト、思い出したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, I remember! Everything that happened back when I was using this notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}You must have buried this notebook so that I'd remember too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:14.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このノートを使っていた時の事…\N海砂も思い出せるように、こっちのノートを埋めてくれたんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, I remember! Everything that happened back when I was using this notebook... You must have buried this notebook so that I'd remember too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, if you're reading this, it's likely that your memory has been restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:20.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君はこの手紙を読み頃には、全てを思い出しているはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter from Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライトからの手紙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember a friend of mine, from Todai University, who introduced himself as "Ryuuga Hideki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:33.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,東応大学で、流河旱樹と名乗った…僕の友人を覚えているか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to write his real name in this notebook and bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:37.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼の本名をノートに書き、葬って欲しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:42.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてこの手紙はすぐに燃やし、\Nノートも数ページだけを隠し持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, as soon as possible, burn this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Take only a few pages from the notebook, and re-bury the notebook itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノート自体が埋めておくように…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time you see me, touch me with a piece of paper from this notebook as naturally as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:50.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと次に僕に会った時、\Nノートの切れ端を自然に触れさせてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can obey me in all this... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll love you, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:54.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これに従ってくれたら、僕は弥海砂を…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can obey me in all this... I'll love you, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}________________________{\alpha&H00&}...love you, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生愛す
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:57.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This is all Light's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか、これがライトの計画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For me to obtain this notebook and regain my memory... {\alpha&HFF&}and kill Ryuuga Hideki... Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂にこのノートを持たせ、記憶を戻し
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For me to obtain this notebook and regain my memory... and kill Ryuuga Hideki... {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流河旱樹…竜崎を殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For me to obtain this notebook and regain my memory... and kill Ryuuga Hideki... Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This should remove another obstacle for Light, and I'll have helped him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:15.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでライトの障害がひとつ消え、海砂はライトの力になれて…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだよ…ライト
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good, Light. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名前なんて覚えてないよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good, Light. I can't remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to see tens, hundreds of names and lifespans every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一日何十人、何百人の人の名前と寿命が見えてたんだもん…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あーーー!!どうやっても思い出せない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can remember! {\alpha&HFF&}Stupid Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can remember! Stupid Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂の馬鹿ーー
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally! I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっとこっちに戻ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk! It's so good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:41.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リューク！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:44.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,久しぶり、元気だった？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm, sorry but... {\alpha&HFF&}being male and all that... that kinda makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:46.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いが…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一応オレもオス、照れる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm, sorry but... being male and all that... {\alpha&HFF&}that kinda makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm, sorry but... being male and all that... that kinda makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あははは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ、そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:55.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Light told me to bring it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライトが持ってけって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなにおいしい？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:03.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Apples in the human world are... how d'ya say it? "Juicy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間界のリンゴはジューシー…って言うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかくうまい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, they're damned good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna try eating one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂も食ってみる？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an apple from the world of Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死神界のリンゴだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいしくなさそう…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look very tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:21.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁまぁ、一口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, Ryuk. {\alpha&HFF&}I want to trade eyes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと、そうだリューク
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, Ryuk. I want to trade eyes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしと目の取引して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,砂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna make a deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取引か？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize that you've already made a deal with Rem once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかってるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:47.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おまえ一度レムと取引してるんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your remaining lifespan has already been halved once; {\alpha&HFF&}you sure you wanna do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:52.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,半分にした残りの寿命を、また半分にしていいんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your remaining lifespan has already been halved once; you sure you wanna do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ、それは仕方ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've completely forgotten the one name that I needed to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:59.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたし覚えてなくちゃいけない\N名前すっかりと忘れてしちゃってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Light will be mad at me unless I go and find it out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,迎えみてくんないとライトに怒られちゃうもん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:06.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ、オレはいいけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ、ミサミサだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing. We can't switch our cell phones on in here, so Misa-Misa has to come all the way here, just to see Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:19.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,可哀想に、ここじゃ携帯の電源も入れられないから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ミサミサの方から訪ねて来るしかないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, hurry up and go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月、早く行ってあげなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't keep a lady waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女性を待たすものではない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:28.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk! {\alpha&HFF&}Why is he with Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:34.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リューク…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何故海砂に憑いている…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk! Why is he with Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa's lifespan has halved again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:44.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂の寿命がさらに半分に減っている…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely she didn't trade eyes with Ryuk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:48.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか…リュークと目の取引を…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:51.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライト
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,久し振りだな、リューク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,L-{\alpha&HFF&}Light, I'm so sorry. I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラ…ライト、ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Light, I'm so sorry. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Light, I'm so sorry. I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, {\alpha&HFF&}no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:10.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流河旱樹の名前覚えてない…どうしても思い出せない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Light, I'm so sorry. I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…残念だな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}But I traded eyes with Ryuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で…でも、リュークと目の取引したから…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I traded eyes with Ryuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all going according to plan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ては計算か…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! {\alpha&HFF&}That means your lifespan has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬鹿…そんなことしたら、寿命が…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! That means your lifespan has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううん、いいの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライトの役に立ちたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}I want to be with you in an ideal world for as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:30.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, I want to be with you in an ideal world for as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:34.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の僕は、君と長く理想の世界で生きたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way I feel, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう気持ちなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライト、嬉しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}let's build a new world together... a world without criminals, filled only with kind-hearted people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:39.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海砂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, let's build a new world together... {\alpha&HFF&}a world without criminals, filled only with kind-hearted people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:45.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二人で犯罪のない、\N優しい人間だけの…新しい世界を創っていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, let's build a new world together... a world without criminals, filled only with kind-hearted people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:46.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
